text: Evangelia Psarra is an archer from Greece. She was born on 17 June 1974. Psarra competed at the 2000, 2004, 2008, 2012, 2016, and the 2020 Summer Olympics,Evangelia PsarraEvangelia PSARRA == References == Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Greek archers Category:Olympians for Greece
